    |  Y POTION  |  START PAUSE  |  BACK / SELECT SHOP  |  REMAP: OVERVIEW > CONTROLS

    KEYBOARD:
    ARROWS / A-D MOVE  |  SHIFT RUN + SPACE JUMP  |  UP / W INTERACT / PARACHUTE 
